<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p>I usually listen to hiphop/rap, but I always do this thing where I find one artist I like and listen to almost exclusively their music for like a month until I find something else and repeat the cycle.</p> <p>I always wondered if this was related to ADHD or if this is just how I am.</p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Wace-Mindu"> /u/Wace-Mindu </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ADHD/comments/bwssgo/i_feel_like_my_my_adhd_affects_my_music_taste/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ADHD/comments/bwssgo/i_feel_like_my_my_adhd_affects_my_music_taste/">[comments]</a></span>